#18250
Elysium of the Traditions~
You are standing in a vast gathering hall, fine draperies and carpeting
cover this place.  It has the look of a library, as there are massive
shelves with countless books here.  You can make out various theorums of the
various traditions, everything from the Virtual Adepts 'The Digital Web,
version 2.  5' to the Euthanatos and their Philosphies of Death and Life.
Torchlight drapes this place in a peaceful aura, and you as continue to look
about, you find that in one corner of this place, the light does not touch.
Instead a flickering green light is here, where the Nephandus go.  All walks
of Magi are Welcome here, including the Technocratic Union.  This is the
Elysium of the Magi, where all may walk in peace.
~
