#18251
The Horizon Realm of the Enlightened~
Colours swirl in all fashions here, the floor, the ceiling, everything is
made of hues of violet, blue, and pink, a thousand other shades of colors
that mankind will never know.  You have stepped onto one of the many facets
of the Horizon realms, where no man will ever step foot.  This place is
where the more Enlightened magi call home, to share discoveries and other
things that they would.
~
