#18252
Library of the Ascended~
This place appears to be the most serene place you would ever find on
earth, or anywhere.  It has the warm feeling that heaven would bring, to a
man who was saved and went into the light.  Those Magi who truly Ascended,
and have escaped the daily chores that are life and apprenticeship rest
here, to contemplate higher philosphies and notions, to increase the
knowledge of their students and themselves.  But strange about this place is
the pillars of this room have veins.  Strange green pulsating veins, and a
strange, beating sound fills your eardrums, like the heart of a unawakened
God...
~
