#18261
A classroom~
This room is filled with desks and shelves lined with books on Mage
Combat.  On a chalkboard you see the following written.  "Greetings,
students.  I am your Professor, Mortimer Temporis.  You may thumb through
the following books in here to gain some insight on your beginning works.
'Bomb', 'AreaBomb' 'Heal'.  By typing 'look bomb', you will see an example
of one so that you will know what to do.  Do not forget to 'cast major rune
mastery', beforehand, then 'cast copy rune page' Before preparing any spell
to be written.  This is very important, or else it will not work.  Please
read all of these books before moving on to the next class room"
~
