E
bomb~
#CThe Basics of a Bomb:#n

The maximum normal damage attainable on a bomb is 4500 damage.
The following is an example of something you could use on one page.
Keep in mind to experiment for better damage ratios for low mana.

write page title #0Dual Lazer Cannons#n(local)
wr start.damage.spell
wr victim.target
wr min.damage: 500
wr max.damage: 1000
wr message.1: #0Dual-lazer Cannons#n
wr message.2: #0From nowhere, a pair of #Ggreen-hued#0 shots are fired, detonating violently#n
wr message.3: #0From nowhere, a pair of #Ggreen-hued#0 shots are fired, detonating violently#n
wr next.page
wr end.spell

Keep in mind that if you do not add 'global.target' under victim.target, you cannot target things
outside of your room.  The 'wr' is just an alias for 'write page line',
which is the key command to write things onto a page
You may now move on to your next lesson.
~
E
heal~
#CThe Basics of  Heal#n

write page title #0Healing of the Lichtouch#n
wr start.damage.spell
wr victim.target
wr reversed
wr min.damage: 300
wr max.damage: 300
wr message.1: #0Lichtouch#n
wr message.2: #0$N#n begins mumbling to herself, and a stale black dust falls ...
wr message.3: #0$N#n begins mumbling to herself, and a stale black dust falls ...
wr end.spell
Okay, also keep in mind it must have 'global.target' beneath 'victim.target'
to work at all.  It also needs a 'next.page' above 'end.spell' in order to
be chained with other pages.  This like any other goes to 15. You may
proceed.
~
E
areabomb~
#CBasics of an Area Bomb#n

write page title #0 Coincidentallightning#n (Pk area)
wr Start.damage.spell
wr area.affect
wr not.caster
wr min.damage: 202
wr max.damage: 202
wr message.1:  #0Coincidental Lightning#n
wr message.2:  The ground sizzles as #0thunder#n and #0lightning#n strike in a chaotic fashion
wr message.3:  The ground sizzles as #0thunder#n and #0lightning#n strike in a chaotic fashion
wr next.page
wr end.spell

Okay, a word on Area bombs. Below 'not.caster' can be 'no.players'. If you do this, it will
become an exp bomb.   Removing this line makes it a PK bomb, and will hit
everything.  in the room, whether you know it is there or not.  This
includes everything, including kakusu, obfuscate, the works.   Do keep
this in mind and use discretion when possible.
~
