Another Classroom~
You walk into a class room much like the other you were in.  Upon the
chalkboard, the following is written: "Welcome, my students.  I am Philesty
Kinestr, the Professor of this workshop on Training, Blessing, and various
affects.  If you type 'Look bless', 'look train', 'look desanct', and 'look
move', I believe you will find these very useful in your quest for
knowledge.  Please, by all means procede"
